text:
Facts about the #TrumpShutdown:
-It didn’t have to happen
-Republicans had months to avert it
-Americans deserve better

The American people deserve certainty in their government & shutting down is not the answer. Offering funding solutions on a month to month basis is not a way to govern. Republicans need to stop hiding from important issues we were sent here to work on.
About to be live on the air with @baxandobrien on @tweetRock102. Tune in now.

A few things we don't know about the Senate #GOPTaxBill:

-What's the dynamic score from the nonpartisan Joint Committee on Taxation?
-How will the SALT provision be paid for?
-How this bill will affect President Trump’s taxes?
On this Thanksgiving, I am thankful to serve the people of the state of Massachusetts. Happy Thanksgiving to you and your families.

#GOPTaxScam eliminates:
   
  -medical expenses deduction
  -adoption tax credit
  -student loan deduction
   
RT if you oppose.
Waking up to news of tragedy in #LasVegas leaves me heartbroken for the victims, families & friends. Thankful for brave 1st responders.
It's a stunning day #intheberkshires. On my way to #NorthAdams for the 62nd Annual Fall Foliage Parade.
At this critical time, I am pleased that President Trump promised not to eliminate the Northern Ireland Special Envoy during our mtg today.
Those w/ loved ones in #PuertoRico or in the path of #HurricaneMaria can contact @StateDept at 1-888-407-4747 or 1-202-501-4444 (overseas).
Members of my staff will be holding office hours TOMORROW at #Pittsfield City Hall from 9-10:30am & #Peru Town Hall from 3-4:30pm.
Trump's decision to end #DACA is disgraceful. These individuals are our neighbors, friends, & family members.
I offer my sincere condolences to the family of fallen officer & Cathedral HS grad Dustin Doyon. I'm grateful for his remarkable service.
Thinking of the missing sailors of the U.S.S. John McCain. I join every American in hoping for a successful rescue mission.
My thoughts and prayers are with the victims of the senseless terrorist attack in Barcelona. We stand in solidarity with the people of Spain
The bigotry, hatred & intolerance in #Charlottesville is wrong & contrary to core American values. There is no place for racism in society.
Skillful diplomacy is needed to lower tensions with #NorthKorea. Not confrontational and aggressive rhetoric.
At 10am and 6pm today I'll be on @cspan Newsmakers discussing #taxreform.
On my way to #WorcesterCounty today. See you soon #Warren & #Sturbridge.
Today we celebrate the 52nd anniversary of #Medicare & #Medicaid and vow to protect them for all American families.
Trump’s decision to ban transgender Americans from serving in the military is wrong & contrary to our core values.
Staff from my office will be hosting office hours in the Law Library on the first floor of the #NorthAdams City Hall on 7/27 from 4-6pm.
My thoughts are w @SenJohnMcCain & his family. John has overcome adversity before & I know the American people extend their best wishes.
The American people honor the service of the brave men and women of the armed forces who put their lives at risk each day for country.
My thoughts and prayers are with the families of the 16 Marines who were killed today when their plane crashed in Mississippi.
See you tomorrow in #Chesterfield for the 70th Annual July 4th Parade.
On the road today to #GreatBarrington #Williamstown & #NorthAdams to announce crucial @EPA & @DHSgov grants to communities & fire stations.
Thankful to the @CapitolPolice & other law enforcement officers who help keep us safe. Speedy recovery for @SteveScalise staffers & police.
Thinking of those affected by the bombing in #Manchester tonight. I will continue to monitor this situation closely as more facts come out.
Reports that @POTUS shared highly classified information with Russian officials should be of great concern to every American.
POTUS has now fired FBI Director. Acting AG and US Atty investigated his ties to #Russia. We need independent investigation now.
Productive meeting with @FranklinCOG talking rural issues, strategies, and growth. Thank you for having me.
Thank you to the residents of #MA01 for calling and voicing your opposition to #TrumpCare. I urge my colleagues to #VoteNoAHCA along with me
Yesterday @SenWarren @SenMarkey and I wrote to Charter & WWLP urging them to negotiate a deal to keep MA news #intheBerkshires.
My friend @HillaryClinton said "Human rights are women’s rights & women’s rights are human rights." I stand with you. #BeBoldForChange #IWD
I'll be visiting #Conway at 3:30pm this afternoon with @repstevekulik to view the aftermath of the tornado and offer assistance to residents
Reports that #Sessions mislead Congress abt his contacts w #Russia reinforce my belief that we need an investigation into Trump-Kremlin ties
Looking forward to hearing from the President at the #JointSession tonight w/ my guest @ShannonYoung413 of @MassLiveNews #notanenemy
Joined my colleagues in advising @DHSgov & @TheJusticeDept to urgently assess the anonymous threats at #JCCs nationwide. This must stop.
I take exception to @POTUS unfortunate remarks. No moral equivalence between U.S. and Putin’s Russia.
I'm on @SquawkCNBC tomorrow at 8:30am talking #taxreform and giving an update from Washington.
.@SallyQYates did not betray Pres Trump, she had the audacity to tell him his travel ban is unlawful. I admire her integrity & courage.
Martin McGuinness may be stepping aside frm politics but his remarkable work in Ireland & across the globe will be remembered for many years
I am always proud to stand with John Lewis.
His extraordinary courage has made our country a better and more inclusive place. And his quiet dignity has been a source of inspiration.
John Lewis has been my good friend and colleague for nearly 30 years. He is a Civil Rights icon and an American hero.
Join me tomorrow on @MSNBC @Morning_Joe at 7:30AM for an update from Washington as we begin the #115thCongress
Pleased to see the Administration is not moving forward with the proposed #Medicare Part B demonstration.
I strongly support a bipartisan congressional investigation into Russia's cyberattacks on the US & its involvement in the 2016 election
In the four years since the #SandyHook tragedy, 130,000 have died from gun violence. #EndGunViolence #HonorWithAction
I'm looking forward to heading back to Washington today for the last month and a half of the #114thCongress.
On behalf of the United States, thank you to our #Veterans. We are so grateful for your service & sacrifices yesterday, today, & tomorrow.
Looking forward to touring farms in #Leyden #Shelburne #Colrain & #Hawley with @USDA tomorrow. Glad to see the foliage has held on
Introduced STOP Act w/ @PatTiberi to stop dangerous synthetic drugs from being shipped thru our borders to drug traffickers here in the US.
Great announcement of @DHSgov #AFG monies to the fire depts in #NorthAdams ($174,373) & #Cheshire ($20,555) today #safetyfirst
In honor of @NatlParkService 100th birthday, I urge you to #FindYourPark and explore right in your own backyard at @SPARNHS #NPS100
Announced $147,456 #USDOJ grant for @SPD_HQ w/ Mayor Sarno today to expand comms & technology, & to increase officer safety & efficiency.
Looking forward to visiting Great Barrington on Monday morning to announce federal grant for the Fire Department.
I am proud the House acted today to tackle the #opioid crisis that has been increasingly plaguing communities around the country & in #CD1
This senseless & terrifying act of violence has no place in a civilized society & is an affront to our core values, morals & beliefs #Dallas
Open invitation to @jk_rowling to tour Mt. Greylock & #Ilvermorny. It's a beautiful time to be #intheberkshires (cc: @SenMarkey @SenWarren)
We need to feel safe at school church work & social events. It's time to reduce the level of gun violence plaguing every corner of America.
Relationship between US & #India is the world’s defining partnership of the 21st Century. TY @narendramodi for his address to Congress today
Join me today at 1pm at the @SpfldMuseums for a Reflection on the #EasterRising, exactly 100 years later.
I'll be LIVE on the @adamwrightshow on @WHYN560 tomorrow at 8:05am
Into'd legislation yesterday that would have the @USTreasury mint coins in commemoration of @Hoophall's 60th anniversary
Expressing my support to Geraldine Finucane and her call for an independent inquiry into her husband’s death @RelsforJustice #PatFinucane
I'll be on @adamwrightshow on @WHYN560 tomorrow at 7:35am to give a preview of #heroin screening.
Tomorrow at 8:05am, I'm live with @baxandobrien on @tweetRock102
I have always been proud @BenjaminDowning is among my distinguished alumni - a thoughtful person & great friend. Thank you, Ben & good luck
I'll be on @WBUR at 3pm today discussing @MassGovernor's first #SOTC tonight & giving an update from Washington.
As we celebrate #MLKDay, let us remember Dr. King's commitment to nonviolence & service to others today & in our everyday lives.
Tomorrow on @adamwrightshow @WHYN560 at 8:05am discussing #heroin speech and #retirement saving legislation
First Garden of Remembrance in US in recognition of 100th Anniversary of 1916 Easter Rising in #Ireland was unveiled today in #Springfield

Thanks for having me Friday MT @Jacobspillow @RepRichardNeal visiting to talk abt @NEAarts grants & importance of arts funding #artmatters
Go @ussoccer! #1N1T #IBelieveThatWeWillWin

The bombs meant to terrorize our community one year ago have only brought us closer together. We will continue to remain #BostonStrong
On this day in 1968, #MLK was tragically taken. While his voice was silenced, his powerful message continues to inspire  around the world.

(2/3) I'll continue to be a strong & outspoken advocate for the ppl of greater North Adams
